---
import { Check, ArrowRight, AlertCircle } from "lucide-react";
---

<section
    class="py-24 bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 border-t border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-800"
>
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6">
        <div class="text-center mb-16">
            <div
                class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-3 py-1 rounded-full bg-purple-100 dark:bg-purple-900/30 text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-300 text-xs font-bold uppercase tracking-wide mb-4"
            >
                Project Spotlight
            </div>
            <h2
                class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4"
            >
                Need a fresh start before committing to a monthly plan?
            </h2>
            <p
                class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg max-w-2xl mx-auto"
            >
                Get your digital house in order with the Google Workspace Reset.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div
            class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center bg-slate-50 dark:bg-slate-800 rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-12 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700"
        >
            {/* Left Column: The Pain */}
            <div>
                <h3
                    class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6"
                >
                    Is this you?
                </h3>
                <ul class="space-y-4">
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold"
                                >?</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg">
                            Are you strictly using a free <span
                                class="font-mono text-slate-500"
                                >@gmail.com</span
                            > address?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold"
                                >?</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg">
                            Or do you have a business email, but the system
                            feels clunky and disconnected?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold"
                                >?</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg">
                            Do you worry your emails are landing in Spam
                            folders?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                    <li class="flex items-start gap-4">
                        <div
                            class="w-8 h-8 rounded-full bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900/20 flex items-center justify-center shrink-0 mt-0.5"
                        >
                            <span
                                class="text-red-600 dark:text-red-400 font-bold"
                                >?</span
                            >
                        </div>
                        <p class="text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 text-lg">
                            Is your Google Drive a mess of untitled files?
                        </p>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>

            {/* Right Column: The Solution */}
            <div class="relative">
                <div
                    class="absolute inset-0 bg-purple-600 blur-[60px] opacity-10 rounded-full"
                >
                </div>
                <div
                    class="relative bg-white dark:bg-slate-900 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-slate-200 dark:border-slate-700 shadow-xl"
                >
                    <div class="flex justify-between items-start mb-6">
                        <div>
                            <h3
                                class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white"
                            >
                                Google Workspace Reset
                            </h3>
                            <p
                                class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm"
                            >
                                One-off Setup Project
                            </p>
                        </div>
                        <div
                            class="text-3xl font-bold text-purple-600 dark:text-purple-400"
                        >
                            Â£500
                        </div>
                    </div>

                    <ul class="space-y-3 mb-8">
                        <li
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                        >
                            <Check className="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" />
                            <span>Full Google Workspace Configuration</span>
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                        >
                            <Check className="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" />
                            {/* Changed to be clear about who owns it */}
                            <span>Connection to your existing Domain</span>
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                        >
                            <Check className="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" />
                            <span>Security & Deliverability (SPF/DKIM)</span>
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                        >
                            <Check className="w-5 h-5 text-green-500" />
                            <span>Email & File Migration (Outlook/Gmail)</span>
                        </li>
                        <li
                            class="flex items-center gap-3 text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300"
                        >
                            <Check className="w-5 h-5 text-purple-500" />
                            <span
                                class="font-bold text-purple-700 dark:text-purple-400"
                                >Bonus: 15-min training video</span
                            >
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <a
                        href="/contact"
                        class="flex items-center justify-center w-full py-4 bg-purple-600 hover:bg-purple-700 text-white font-bold rounded-xl transition-colors group mb-4"
                    >
                        Get Your Reset <ArrowRight
                            className="w-4 h-4 ml-2 group-hover:translate-x-1 transition-transform"
                        />
                    </a>

                    {/* The Disclaimer you needed */}
                    <div
                        class="flex gap-2 text-xs text-slate-400 dark:text-slate-500 leading-tight"
                    >
                        <AlertCircle className="w-4 h-4 shrink-0" />
                        <p>
                            Does not include Google subscription or domain
                            purchase fees.
                        </p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
